data.title: Vans Tongue Lockdown System | Fashion | VANS
data.description:
Tongue Lock Down: Featured on the V66 and Sequal the Tongue Lock Down system pulls the tongue down as you tighten your boots helping to eliminate heel lift while also improving lacing efficiency above the instep.

Music: "Midnight Summer Scheme" by Zac Marben

About Vans:
Vans®, a VF Corporation (NYSE: VFC) brand, is the original action sports footwear, apparel and accessories brand. Vans also owns and operates more than 450 retail locations around the world. The Vans brand promotes the action sports lifestyle, youth culture and creative self-expression through the support of athletes, musicians and artists and through progressive events and platforms such as the Vans Triple Crown of Surfing®, the Vans U.S. Open of Surfing, Vans Pool Party, Vans Custom Culture, Vans Warped Tour®, and Vans’ cultural hub and international music venue, the House of Vans.

data.title: Vans Women's Aura Snowboard Boot | Snow | VANS
data.description:
W Aura: The Aura combines a clean and classic aesthetic with advanced features giving you the ultimate blend of style and performance. 
The Aura features adjustable zonal closure with a custom slide guide that allows female riders to tune the direction of pull in the instep which is critical for both comfort and eliminating response stealing heel lift. 
All of this wrapped up in a lightweight low profile silhouette designed around a lower calf and narrower ankle pocket that define a truly women’s specific fit.

Music: "Midnight Summer Scheme" by Zac Marben
